# AgriShield Blockchain — Environment Variables Reference
#
# ─── IMPORTANT ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This project uses Hardhat v3, which manages secrets via its own variable store
# instead of a .env file. Use the commands below to set your secrets securely.
#
# ─── SET YOUR SECRETS (run these once from the blockchain/ folder) ────────────
#
#   npx hardhat vars set SEPOLIA_RPC_URL    https://eth-sepolia.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_KEY
#   npx hardhat vars set SEPOLIA_PRIVATE_KEY 0xYOUR_PRIVATE_KEY
#
# Secrets are stored in ~/.hardhat/vars.json  (never committed to git)
#
# ─── WHERE TO GET THESE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#   SEPOLIA_RPC_URL:
#     Sign up at https://alchemy.com → Create App → Ethereum → Sepolia
#     Copy the HTTPS endpoint URL
#
#   SEPOLIA_PRIVATE_KEY:
#     ⚠️  Use a DEDICATED deployment wallet — never your main wallet
#     MetaMask → Account Details → Export Private Key
#     The key should start with 0x
#
#   Test ETH (Sepolia):
#     https://sepoliafaucet.com  (free, requires Alchemy account)
#
# ─── AFTER DEPLOYMENT ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy the printed contract address into your root .env:
#   VITE_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=0xYOUR_DEPLOYED_CONTRACT_ADDRESS
#
# ─── SECURITY ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ⚠️  NEVER commit your PRIVATE_KEY — ever
# ⚠️  Add this file's actual counterpart (.env) to .gitignore
# ⚠️  blockchain/.env and blockchain/absolute path/.env are in .gitignore

# ─── Variable names (for reference) ──────────────────────────────────────────
SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=
SEPOLIA_PRIVATE_KEY=
